citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b)
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:30pm on
02/26/2014.
Unauthorized person indicated that she would not be home until after 6pm due to work schedule.
